{% set pageTitle = 'NHS service standard' %}
{% set pageDescription = 'The NHS service standard is designed to help digital teams build and run products or services which help improve health outcomes, people&#39;s experience of health and care, and the efficiency of the health service.' %}
{% set noFollow = true %}

{% extends 'includes/layout.njk' %}

{% block body %}
<div class="nhsuk-grid-row">
  <div class="nhsuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1>{{pageTitle}}</h1>
    <p class="nhsuk-body-l">The NHS service standard is designed to help digital teams build and run services that improve health outcomes, people&#39;s experience of health and care, and the efficiency of the health service.</p>
    <p>The standard will help you check that your service is good enough for the NHS.</p>
    <p><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/about">Read more about the standard</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="app-service-standard__type"><span class="app-service-standard__number">A.</span> Meeting users' needs</h2>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h4 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">1.</span> Understand users and their needs in the context of health and care</h4>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/1-understand-users-and-their-needs-context-health-and-care">Read more about point 1.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">2.</span> Join things up and work towards solving a whole problem</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/2-join-things-up-and-work-towards-solving-a-whole-problem">Read more about point 2.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading" id="point3"><span class="app-service-standard__number">3.</span> Make the service easy to use</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/3-make-the-service-easy-to-use">Read more about point 3.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">4.</span> Make sure everyone can use the service</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/4-make-sure-everyone-can-use-the-service">Read more about point 4.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading" id="point5"><span class="app-service-standard__number">5.</span> Support a culture of care</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/5-support-a-culture-of-care">Read more about point 5.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading" id="point6"><span class="app-service-standard__number">6.</span> Make your service clinically safe</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/6-make-your-service-clinically-safe">Read more about point 6.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard app-service-standard--bottom">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">7.</span> Respect and protect users' confidentiality and privacy</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/7-respect-and-protect-users-confidentiality-and-privacy">Read more about point 7.</a></p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="app-service-standard__type"><span class="app-service-standard__number">B.</span> Providing a service</h2>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">8.</span> Create a team that includes multidisciplinary skills and perspectives</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/8-create-a-team-that-includes-multidisciplinary-skills-and-perspectives">Read more about point 8.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">9.</span> Use agile ways of working</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/9-use-agile-ways-of-working">Read more about point 9.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">10.</span> Iterate and improve frequently</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/10-iterate-and-improve-frequently">Read more about point 10.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard app-service-standard--bottom">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">11.</span> Define what success looks like and be open about how your service is performing</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/11-define-what-success-looks-like-and-be-open-about-how-your-service-is-performing">Read more about point 11.</a></p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="app-service-standard__type"><span class="app-service-standard__number">C.</span> Make smart choices about technology</h2>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading" id="point12"><span class="app-service-standard__number">12.</span> Make your service interoperable</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/12-make-your-service-interoperable">Read more about point 12.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">13.</span> Choose the right tools and technology</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/13-choose-the-right-tools-and-technology">Read more about point 13.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">14.</span> Make new source code open</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/14-make-new-source-code-open">Read more about point 14.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">15.</span> Use and contribute to common components and patterns</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/15-use-and-contribute-to-common-components-and-patterns">Read more about point 15.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-service-standard app-service-standard--bottom">
      <h3 class="app-service-standard__heading"><span class="app-service-standard__number">16.</span> Operate a reliable service</h3>
      <p class="app-service-standard__link"><a href="/service-manual/service-standard/16-operate-a-reliable-service">Read more about point 16.</a></p>
    </div>

    <p class="nhsuk-body-s nhsuk-u-margin-top-7">Updated: October 2019</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
